<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_15_su_0002" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3, page_4">
    <section class="title type2 page-1-title">
      <h2 lang="y" data-head="1">
        윤서네 마을에 넓이가 120000 ㎡이면서 둘레가 가장 짧은 직사각형 모양의
        공원을 만들려고 합니다. 만들 수 있는 가장 짧은 공원<br />의 둘레는 몇
        m인지 구해 봅시다.(단, 변의 길이는 100 m씩 늘이거나 줄일 수 있습니다.)
      </h2>
    </section>
    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <article class="page page_1">
        <section class="title type2"></section>
        <h3 lang="y">
          넓이가 120000 ㎡인 서로 다른 직사각형을 3가지 그려 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area po_absolute">
          <div class="question_box dir_col align_start">
            <div class="align_center ">
              <div class="img_area">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_15_SU/15_03_bg.png" alt="배경 이미지" />
                <div class="length1">
                  <span>100 m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="length2">
                  <span>100 m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="length3">
                  <span>10000 ㎠</span>
                </div>
                <div class="canvas-wrap">
                  <div id="square">
                    </di>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_15_SU/15_03_ex1.svg" alt="">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </article>
      <!-- 1page -->

      <article class="page page_2 page2">
        <h3 lang="y">
          내가 그린 직사각형과 친구가 그린 직사각형의 둘레를 비교해 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y">내가 그린 직사각형의 둘레는 각각 2600 m, 1600 m, 1400 m이고, 친구가 그린 직사각형의
                    둘레는 각각 2600 m, 1400 m, 1600 m입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </article>
      <!-- 2page -->
      <article class="page page_3 page3">
        <h3 lang="y">
          표를 완성하여 넓이가 120000 ㎡인 직사각형의 둘레를 모두 구해 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th class="top_table">가로 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="200"></math-field>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="300"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td class="right_table">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1200"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>세로 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1200"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="300"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="200"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="bottom_table">둘레 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td class="radius">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2600"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- 2page -->
      <article class="page page_3">
        <h3 lang="y">만들 수 있는 가장 짧은 공원의 둘레는 몇 m인가요?</h3>
        <div class="flex align_center gap_12 flex_wrap">
          <div class="input_wrap answer1">
            <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="1" text-align="center"></math-field>
            <span>m</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article><!-- 3page -->
      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
